{"ID":"20260609125322-o87qku0","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609125322-o87qku0","title":"2021年新高考Ⅰ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609125333"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609125333-gv5y4cd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125333-gv5y4cd","updated":"20260609125333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"欢快的锣鼓敲起来，欢腾的雄狮舞起来，“闹元宵，学‘四史’”文明实践示范活动日在市文化艺术中心隆重举行，活动分为“四史”猜谜颂红色文化、非遗展示传民俗文化、戏曲联唱扬传统文化三个篇章，民俗与党史彼此交融，传统与现代"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125333-bmk1gck","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125333-bmk1gck","updated":"20260609125333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"元宵线上活动直播间里"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，一场关于党史知识和传统民俗知识的直播宣讲“圈粉”无数，辖区党员，青年志愿者以及现场观众"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"地进入直播间，感受节目的欢快气氛。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"宣讲员平易的话语，幽默的口吻以及宣讲内容十分接地气，导致收看直播的群众既听得进又记得牢。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125333-8wrxrhz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125333-8wrxrhz","updated":"20260609125333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"传统文化展现传统节日，传统节日传承传统文化。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"剪纸灯谜，描绘城乡风物；秧歌花鼓，传播时代精神。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"火树银花踏歌行，古风新韵颂文明，一席"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的文明盛宴，让市民近距离感受到传统文化的深厚魅力和传统节日的浓厚氛围。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-9gb5krc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-9gb5krc","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．依次填入文中横线上的词语，全都恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-8okhchh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-8okhchh","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．相互映衬    喧闹无比    络绎不绝    原汁原味"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-axobw0a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-axobw0a","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．相互映衬    热闹非凡    连绵不断    原汁原味"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-1pd0znw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-1pd0znw","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．相互映衬    喧闹无比    连绵不断    汁醇味正"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-ee21lwk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-ee21lwk","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．交相辉映    热闹非凡    络绎不绝    汁醇味正"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-knjhbkb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-knjhbkb","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中画波浪线的句子有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-8qleo56","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-8qleo56","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．宣讲员话语平易，口吻幽默，宣讲内容也十分接地气，这导致收看直播的群众既听得进又记得牢。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-04cp4v9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-04cp4v9","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．宣讲员话语平易，口吻幽默，宣讲内容也十分接地气，导致收看直播的群众既听得进又记得牢。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-juqez0j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-juqez0j","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．宣讲员平易的话语、幽默的口吻以及宣讲内容十分接地气，这使得收看直播的群众既听得进又记得牢。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-ptngpte","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-ptngpte","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．宣讲员平易的话语，幽默的口吻以及十分接地气的宣讲内容，使得收看直播的群众既听得进又记得牢。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125345-bv9736i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125345-bv9736i","updated":"20260609125345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．文中画横线的句子使用了对偶的修辞手法，请简要分析其构成和表达效果。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134707-0l7bslh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134707-0l7bslh","updated":"20260609130234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．下列填入文中括号内的语句，衔接最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609134707-7rqlndp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134707-7rqlndp","updated":"20260609130234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．雪变色是微型藻类雪衣藻大量繁殖的结果"}]},{"ID":"20260609134707-xid3fos","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134707-xid3fos","updated":"20260609130234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．雪变色是因为雪衣藻这种微型藻类的大量繁殖"}]},{"ID":"20260609134707-loz5mnm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134707-loz5mnm","updated":"20260609130234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．微型藻类雪衣藻大量繁殖引起了雪变色"}]},{"ID":"20260609134707-6smxhyf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134707-6smxhyf","updated":"20260609130234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．雪衣藻这种微型藻类大量繁殖引起了雪变色"}]},{"ID":"20260609134707-ie7qasw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134707-ie7qasw","updated":"20260609130234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"22．请在文中横线处补写恰当的语句，使整段文字语意完整连贯，内容贴切，逻辑严密，每处不超过8个字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125322-3w4hpqt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125322-3w4hpqt","updated":"20260609134719"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609125400-a8bb6ai","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125400-a8bb6ai","updated":"20260609125401"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．D    19．D    20．①意义紧密相连。“剪纸灯谜”和“秧歌花鼓”都是传统民间艺术名称，两两相对；“描绘”和“传播”、“城乡”和“时代”、“风物”和“精神”也都是两两相对。②形式整齐，节奏感强，朗朗上口，有助于烘托节日的欢快气氛。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134719-b756lrk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134719-b756lrk","updated":"20260609125504"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．A    22．示例:"}]},{"ID":"20260609134719-bqjz88y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134719-bqjz88y","updated":"20260609125504"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①在寒冷的冬季"}]},{"ID":"20260609134719-sziw8gk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134719-sziw8gk","updated":"20260609125504"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②生长期呈绿色"}]},{"ID":"20260609134719-pkrc42p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134719-pkrc42p","updated":"20260609125504"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③加快融雪速度"}]},{"ID":"20260609125322-auzbafg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125322-auzbafg","updated":"20260609134731"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-p7jylnw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-p7jylnw","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查学生正确使用成语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-g4n05u7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-g4n05u7","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"交相辉映：意指各种光亮、色彩等互相映照。多用于形容美好的景象。互相映衬：是利用客观事物之间相似或相反的关系，以次要形象映照衬托主要形象的写作技法。根据语境“民俗与党史彼此交融”，可知两者是不分主次的，所以“传统和现代”也是不分主次，所以选“交相辉映”合适。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-z9m89ds","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-z9m89ds","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"喧闹无比：是指声音特别嘈杂，周围环境不安静，导致的结果就是人的心里很烦闷，含贬义。热闹非凡：形容热闹的场面或景象。语境是指元宵线上活动直播间里的圈粉无数的火爆场面，选“热闹非凡”合适。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-kfqcd29","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-kfqcd29","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"络绎不绝：用来形容人、马、车、船等连续不断。连绵不断：形容连续不止，一直都不中断。语境是指青年志愿者以及现场观众不断地进入直播间，选“络绎不绝”合适。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-1si7e7v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-1si7e7v","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原汁原味：比喻事物本来的、没有受到外来影响的风格。汁醇味正：形容菜肴美味。根据后文形容的是“文明盛宴”（使用了比喻），照应喻体，选“汁醇味正”合适。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-cz79hg8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-cz79hg8","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-t4d7crg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-t4d7crg","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-68wwgjd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-68wwgjd","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文中画波浪线的句子有两处语病，一是“平易的话语，幽默的口吻以及宣讲内容十分接地气”中，并列成分结构混乱，应该词性相同结构一致，可改为“话语平易，口吻幽默，宣讲内容也十分接地气”，或者“平易的话语，幽默的口吻以及十分接地气的宣讲内容”；二是“导致”使用不当，“导致”后常用于不好的结果，用于“群众既听得进又记得牢”不恰当，可改为“使得”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-zjaju3i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-zjaju3i","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．“导致”使用不当；“这”指代不明确，句子有歧义。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-k97r0mw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-k97r0mw","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．“导致”使用不当。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-m5v3ju4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-m5v3ju4","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．“平易的话语、幽默的口吻以及宣讲内容十分接地气”并列成分结构混乱，令人费解；“这”指代不明确，句子有歧义。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-et8djrr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-et8djrr","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-fr98tgp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-fr98tgp","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．本题考查学生正确使用常见的修辞手法、理解表达效果的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-rtipdkk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-rtipdkk","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对偶的构成从结构、字数、意义、声调等角度去分析，表达效果应结合内容从语言、节奏、感染力、思想内容等角度进行分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-lbl9yha","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-lbl9yha","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“剪纸灯谜，描绘城乡风物；秧歌花鼓，传播时代精神”中“剪纸灯谜”和“秧歌花鼓”都是并列式的名词性词组，且上下联的意思是相近相关的，都是传统节目，对仗非常工整。“描绘城乡风物”和“传播时代精神”都是动宾式结构，“描绘”对“传播”，都是动词，名词“城乡”对应“时代”，名词“风物”对应“精神”，“城乡风物”“时代精神”都是偏正式结构，词性相同，意思相近，且对仗非常工整。上下两句结构相同，内容上相关，构成一组对偶句。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125417-r9ekcmd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125417-r9ekcmd","updated":"20260609125417"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“剪纸灯谜，描绘城乡风物；秧歌花鼓，传播时代精神”运用对偶（对仗）的形式，长短句结合，句式整齐中富有变化，“剪纸灯谜”“秧歌花鼓”均选择了典型的节日活动，由点带面，凝练集中地概括了我国传统节日的节目内容各具特色、缤纷多彩花样繁多的特点，“描绘城乡风物”“传播时代精神”形容传统节日的价值和作用。形式上整齐匀称，节奏感强，抑扬顿挫，音韵和谐，读起来朗朗上口，便于传诵。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-6fnxwao","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-6fnxwao","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"21．本题考查学生语言表达之连贯能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-hgeeln8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-hgeeln8","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"阅读文段，厘清上下语句逻辑关系。上文提到“有研究人员分析”可得出下文需回答雪为什么会变色的原因，叙述主语应为“雪变色”。CD的叙述对象是“雪衣藻”，所以排除CD。再依下文叙述对象是“雪衣藻”得知B中的“雪衣藻这种微型藻类”强调的不是雪衣藻，而是“这种微型藻类”，所以排除B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-d4ulcus","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-d4ulcus","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-1d7m3nd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-1d7m3nd","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"22．本题考查学生语言表达之情境补写的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-krwkjkv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-krwkjkv","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一处，根据上文“它们处于冬眠静止状态”得出这里应填雪衣藻在什么样的条件下会冬眠，而根据后面的“但是一旦阳光足够温暖”可推知，这里应该是说雪衣藻在气温较低的时候会冬眠，所以此处可填“寒冬时节/在寒冷的冬季”。."}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-zxqinog","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-zxqinog","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二空，根据下文“成熟后会产生类胡萝卜素而变为红色”得知，第二空是填雪衣藻不成熟时的颜色。再根据后文“呈现出从绿色到红色”的变化可知，不成熟时的颜色应该是绿色。由此可知，这里可填“最初是绿色/未成熟时是绿色的/年轻时是绿色的”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609134731-bpsvjkq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609134731-bpsvjkq","updated":"20260609125516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三空，根据下文“而融雪速度的加快可能使得极地冰雪消融失控”可知，这是对上文现象产生的结果的阐述，故可推测降低雪反射阳光量会加快了冰雪消融的速度，所以此处应填“加快了融雪的速度”。"}]}]}